# Extension IDs — single source of truth for all builds.
#
# These values are stamped into artifacts at build time:
#
#   ARLOPASS_CHROME_EXTENSION_ID   → bridge installer (native messaging allowed_origins)
#   ARLOPASS_EDGE_EXTENSION_ID     → bridge installer (native messaging allowed_origins)
#   ARLOPASS_FIREFOX_EXTENSION_ID  → extension build (gecko manifest ID) + bridge installer
#
# Local dev:  edit this file (gitignored).
# Production: set as GitHub repository variables (Settings → Variables).

